Title: A PARALLEL RAYCAST ALGORITHM OF CSG MODELS ON CM2  
Author: Piero Pili 
Keyword: Parallel Computing, Computer Graphics, Geometric Modeling, Solid Modeling, CSG Evaluation, RayTracing, Image Synthesis.  
Address: Milano, Italy  
Affiliation: Cad Group, CNR  
Note: International Journal of Modern Physics C c World Scientific Publishing Company  Received (to be inserted Revised by Publisher)  
Abstract: This work presents a parallel algorithm to produce high-quality shaded pictures directly from Constructive Solid Geometry (CSG) in early real time. The algorithm performs a pixel parallelization of the Ray Casting tecnique of CSG models. L'articolo propone un nuovo approccio al problema della parallelizzazione dell'algoritmo di Ray Casting di modelli CSG su architettura SIMD (Connection Machine) . Dopo una breve descrizione del problema affrontato viene presentato l'algoritmo implementato ed irisul-tati ottenuti. 
